<h2 id="tips">Tips</h2>
<ul>
<li>In the top-right corner of the Automation Button popup, click the arrows icon to collapse all step settings to see more steps at once. This also is great when reordering steps.</li>
<li>Click the step name to enter your own description of what the step does. This is a great way to keep complex automations organized.</li>
</ul>
